Package com.example.impostersyndrom.controller

Class EditEmojiResources

java.lang.Object
com.example.impostersyndrom.controller.EditEmojiResources
public class EditEmojiResources extends Object
EditEmojiResources is a utility class that provides methods to retrieve mood-related resources such as colors, descriptions, and drawable resources based on the emoji name.
Author:
Rayan

      Parameters:
